docker-compose up
start app

  <============ What's News =============>
http://localhost:8081/api/v1/feednews           <== Postman : GET ==>  + {header: x-user-id } :

  <============ Get All FeedNews From Scratch =============>
http://localhost:8081/api/v1/heater             <== Postman : GET ==>  + {header: x-user-id }

  <============ PUBLISH <Post> =============>
http://localhost:8081/api/v1/posts/{postId}/publish  <== Postman : PUT ==>  + {header: x-user-id }

  <============ CREATE <Post> =============>
http://localhost:8081/api/v1/posts              <== Postman : POST ==>  + {header: x-user-id }
{
    "content": "Post content must not be blank",
    "hashtagNames": ["#Amazonka_07", "#Bum_Ba_Rash"]
}
  <============ UPDATE <Post> =============>
http://localhost:8081/api/v1/posts              <== Postman : PUT ==>   + {header: x-user-id }
{
    "id": 9,
    "content": "New Post content",
    "hashtagNames": ["#Carrramba79", "#_AliBaBa_99"]
}
  <============ VIEW <Post> =============>
http://localhost:8081/api/v1/posts/{postId}     <== Postman : GET ==>    + {header: x-user-id }

  <============ CREATE <Comment> =============>
http://localhost:8081/api/v1/comments           <== Postman : POST ==>  + {header: x-user-id }
{
     "postId": 9,
     "content": "Comment content must not be blank"
}
  <============ UPDATE <Comment> =============>
http://localhost:8081/api/v1/comments           <== Postman : PUT ==>  + {header: x-user-id }
{
     "id": 5,
     "content": "Update Comment content"
}
  <============ ADD LIKE to <Post> =============>
http://localhost:8081/api/v1/likes/post         <== Postman : POST ==> + {header: x-user-id }
{
   "postId": 9
}
  <============ ADD LIKE to <Comment> =============>
http://localhost:8081/api/v1/likes/comment      <== Postman : POST ==>  + {header: x-user-id }
{
   "commentId": 4
}
  <============ GET LIKEs =============>
## Test get likes to <Post>
http://localhost:8081/api/v1/likes/post/{postId}            <== Postman : GET ==>  + {header: x-user-id }
## Test get likes to <Comment>
http://localhost:8081/api/v1/likes/comment/{commentId}      <== Postman : GET ==>  + {header: x-user-id }

  <============ DELETE LIKEs =============>
## Test delete likes from <Post>
http://localhost:8081/api/v1/likes/post/{postId}/{userId}         <== Postman : DELETE ==>  + {header: x-user-id }
## Test delete likes from <Comment>
http://localhost:8081/api/v1/likes/comment/{commentId}/{userId}   <== Postman : DELETE ==>  + {header: x-user-id }

  <============ GET <Posts> By Hashtag name =============>
http://localhost:8081/api/v1/posts/hashtag                  <== Postman : GET ==>  + {header: x-user-id }
{
    "name": "#adventures_2021"
}
  <============ GET all drafts posts By User =============>
http://localhost:8081/api/v1/posts/drafts/user/{userId}     <== Postman : GET ==>  + {header: x-user-id }

  <============ GET all published Posts By User =============>
http://localhost:8081/api/v1/posts/published/user/{userId}  <== Postman : GET ==>  + {header: x-user-id }

  <============ Create a resource =============>
http://localhost:8081/resources/{postId}     <== Postman : POST ==>




